metadata.name: MyBubble Metaverse Therapy #2
metadata.description:
This is 1 of 10 Monthly Therapy Access NFTs. Once you own one of these MyBubble NFTs, you will have lifetime access to monthly therapy appointments. These will be hosted in the metaverse with qualified psychiatrists and mental health experts. 

This will be the only MyBubble NFT collection of its kind, with one token providing access to mental health support for life. Each NFT is unique, lying on the public Ethereum blockchain (ERC-721). 

In order to book your monthly therapy appointment, join our MyBubble Discord server at https://discord.gg/5dF8hjDbe7 and go to the 'collabland-join' channel to verify ownership of your NFT!
